            <h2 style="font-size: 2em; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 18px; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left;">
                Chameleons in danger!
            </h2>
            <p style="font-size: 1.18em; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; text-align: left;">
                Nearly <strong style="color: var(--important-text); font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.2em;">38%</strong> of chameleons are at risk of extinction. The destruction of their forests and global warming are making their survival increasingly difficult.<br>
                Protecting nature also means saving these incredible lizards.
            </p>
